data.description: Incredible opportunity! MOTIVATED SELLER! Well kept, centrally located 4 bed/2 bath pool home in quiet residential area with easy Ft. Myers access. Walking distance to shopping, restaurants, groceries, and firehouse. Over 2000 sq ft. of living space with stylish tile and laminate flooring. Open floor plan offers eat-in kitchen with large island and breakfast bar, plus a BONUS room for formal dining or home office. Dedicated laundry room leads to garage with built-in workbench and storage. Screened lanai is surrounded by fenced yard, with dog run and tropical landscaping. King-sized master suite offers walk-in closet and bath with soaking tub, separate shower, and door leading out to pool. Comes with Home Warranty and all appliances. Updates: new roof-2019, inground pool resurfaced to include interior upgraded lip tile-2019, HVAC blower motor-2020/evaporator coil-2023, home solar electrical system-2021, hot water heater-2022, pool timer and filter system-2023, garage door opener-2023, and smoke detectors-2023. All central utility assessments are paid on this lovely home (savings of up to $35,000 for buyer). Call for a showing and turn this dream home into your Florida dream home!
